          <td>[Painful/Non-painful]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Mastoid Tenderness:</td>
          <td>[Present/Absent]</td>
          <td>[Present/Absent]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Pre-auricular/Post-auricular Swelling:</td>
          <td>[Consistency, Tenderness, Fluctuation]</td>
          <td>[Consistency, Tenderness, Fluctuation]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>HEARING ASSESSMENT (Basic):</strong></td>
          <td><br>
          </td>
          <td><br>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Whisper Test / Conversational Voice:</td>
          <td>[Normal/Reduced]</td>
          <td>[Normal/Reduced]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Tuning Fork Tests (Rinne's):</td>
          <td colspan="2">[Describe Rinne's for each ear]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Tuning Fork Tests (Weber's):</td>
          <td colspan="2">[Describe Weber's for each ear] lateralization, ABC
            comparison]</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Tuning Fork Tests (ABC):</td>
          <td colspan="2">[Describe ABC for each ear]</td>
